tp://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"TheParis Olympicsare\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 816}, {\"ngram\": \"the groove\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 840}, {\"ngram\": \"the historic opening ceremony\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 874}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dancers who will jazz upthe July 26 showunder the artistic direction of prize-winning French theater directorThomas Jollyare putting finishing touches on a high-octane performance that will combine urban, contemporary, classic, and break dancing, complete with stomps, shouts, and body rolls.\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 1188, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 982, \"end\": 996, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Theatre_of_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.923210660155397e-17, \"text\": \"French theater\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Theatre_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Theatre_of_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dancers\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 903}, {\"ngram\": \"upthe\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 923}, {\"ngram\": \"the artistic direction\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 964}, {\"ngram\": \"Jollyare\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1020}, {\"ngram\": \"finishing touches\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1046}, {\"ngram\": \"a high-octane performance\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1075}, {\"ngram\": \"stomps\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1163}, {\"ngram\": \"shouts\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1171}, {\"ngram\": \"body rolls\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1187}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Associated Press got a behind-the-scenes look of one of their rehearsals, providing an advance peek into preparations for the opening show that is largely shrouded in secrecy.\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1369, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1194, \"end\": 1210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999438564627311, \"rank\": 5.6146689508970936e-05, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the-scenes\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1234}, {\"ngram\": \"their rehearsals\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1266}, {\"ngram\": \"an advance peek\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1293}, {\"ngram\": \"preparations\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1311}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening show\", \"from\": 1316, \"to\": 1332}, {\"ngram\": \"secrecy\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1368}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dance director Maud Le Pladec instructed around 50 dancers on their twists and turns at a warehouse in the northern Parisian suburb of Saint-Denis.\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1517, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dance director Maud Le Pladec\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1399}, {\"ngram\": \"around 50 dancers\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1428}, {\"ngram\": \"their twists\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1444}, {\"ngram\": \"a warehouse\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1469}, {\"ngram\": \"the northern Parisian suburb\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1501}, {\"ngram\": \"Saint-Denis\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1516}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She spoke with pride of the rich cultural mix of her melting-pot troupe, declaring: \\\"It represents the part of France I love.\\\"\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1644, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1629, \"end\": 1635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999979391889927, \"rank\": 1.9154681783678475e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pride\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1538}, {\"ngram\": \"the rich cultural mix\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1563}, {\"ngram\": \"her melting-pot troupe\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1589}, {\"ngram\": \"the part\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1625}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are in France but we are talking to the whole world,\\\" she said, \\\"which means we have different identities, bodies, ages.\\\"\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1771, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1657, \"end\": 1663, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999979391889927, \"rank\": 1.9154681783678475e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the whole world\", \"from\": 1686, \"to\": 1701}, {\"ngram\": \"different identities\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1755}, {\"ngram\": \"bodies\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1763}, {\"ngram\": \"ages\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1769}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The grandiose open-air ceremony will beheld during sunsetand is expected to last nearly four hours, transforming the heart of Paris and its iconic landmarks into a giant stage for Jolly's artistic talents but also requiring a massive security effort.\", \"from\": 1773, \"to\": 2023, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1899, \"end\": 1904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8510267320852327e-28, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The grandiose open-air ceremony\", \"from\": 1773, \"to\": 1804}, {\"ngram\": \"sunsetand\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 1833}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly four hours\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 1871}, {\"ngram\": \"the heart\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1895}, {\"ngram\": \"its iconic landmarks\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 1929}, {\"ngram\": \"a giant stage\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 1948}, {\"ngram\": \"Jolly's artistic talents\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 1977}, {\"ngram\": \"a massive security effort\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2022}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"An opening ceremony has never been held outside of a stadium.\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2087, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An opening ceremony\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2045}, {\"ngram\": \"a stadium\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2086}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is no model, it's absolute creation,\\\" Jolly said in an interview published Tuesday by Le Parisien newspaper.\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2180, \"end\": 2191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Parisien\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Le Parisien\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Parisien\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Parisien\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no model\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2105}, {\"ngram\": \"absolute creation\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2129}, {\"ngram\": \"Jolly\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2137}, {\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2158}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Detailing how he's had to revisit some of his ideas to fit the urban environment, Jolly said he'd imagined having a giant ballet with 200 dancers on one of the bridges that span the Seine but, after a study was done, \\\"we were told that everyone doing the same step at the same time would endanger the bridge's solidity.\\\"\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2524, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2386, \"end\": 2391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2344745865403984e-23, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his ideas\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2255}, {\"ngram\": \"the urban environment\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2284}, {\"ngram\": \"Jolly\", \"from\": 2286, \"to\": 2291}, {\"ngram\": \"a giant ballet\", \"from\": 2318, \"to\": 2332}, {\"ngram\": \"200 dancers\", \"from\": 2338, \"to\": 2349}, {\"ngram\": \"the bridges\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2371}, {\"ngram\": \"a study\", \"from\": 2403, \"to\": 2410}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2448}, {\"ngram\": \"the same step\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2468}, {\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 2472, \"to\": 2485}, {\"ngram\": \"the bridge's solidity\", \"from\": 2501, \"to\": 2522}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also said: \\\"I wanted to build an upside-down Eiffel Tower.\", \"from\": 2526, \"to\": 2587, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an upside-down Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2586}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I thought it would be pretty for lighting the Olympic flame.\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2648, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic flame\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2647}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it wasn't doable.\\\"\", \"from\": 2649, \"to\": 2671, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The initial overall concept for the ceremony has had to be adapted \\\"so that the dream and the reality meet,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2791, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The initial overall concept\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2700}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 2705, \"to\": 2717}, {\"ngram\": \"the dream\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 2758}, {\"ngram\": \"the reality meet\", \"from\": 2763, \"to\": 2779}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For security services,the unprecedented decisionto parade thousands of Olympians on boats along a 6-kilometer (3.7-mile) stretch ofthe Seine, from Pont d'Austerlitz to Pont d'I\\u00e9na, in front of a 320,000-strong crowd is a huge challenge.\", \"from\": 2793, \"to\": 3029, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2928, \"end\": 2933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2344745865403984e-23, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 2940, \"end\": 2957, \"title\":